'''开放民主网'''（{{lang-en|openDemocracy}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2019/9/14/balfour-brexit-britain-improvisational-politics-misfortunes|title=从《贝尔福宣言》到脱欧 英国与即兴政治的不幸|date=2019年9月14日|publisher=[[半岛电视台|半岛电视台]]|access-date=2020年7月4日|archive-date=2020年8月21日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200821095059/https://chinese.aljazeera.net/news/2019/9/14/balfour-brexit-britain-improvisational-politics-misfortunes}}</ref>）是一家总部位于[[英国|英国]]的[[政治|政治]][[网站|网站]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3067242|title=华为砸钱5G「置入性」研究 染指LSE学术自由和校誉|date=2020-02-13|publisher=[[自由时报|自由时报]]|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-05-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524212304/https://ec.ltn.com.tw/article/breakingnews/3067242}}</ref>，于2001年5月作为一个“试点”项目<ref name="Curran2011">{{cite book|author=James Curran|title=Media and Democracy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=JbwQ9OeVSMgC&pg=PA86|date=31 March 2011|publisher=Taylor & Francis|isbn=978-1-134-37223-2|pages=86–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-11-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211103225619/https://books.google.com/books?id=JbwQ9OeVSMgC&pg=PA86}}</ref>由安东尼·巴尼特（Anthony Barnett<ref name="WestallGardiner2013">{{cite book|author1=C. Westall|author2=M. Gardiner|title=Literature of an Independent England: Revisions of England, Englishness and English Literature|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DW80AAAAQBAJ&pg=PR8|date=9 July 2013|publisher=Springer|isbn=978-1-137-03524-0|pages=8–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001011420/https://books.google.com/books?id=DW80AAAAQBAJ&pg=PR8}}</ref>）、大卫·海斯（David Hayes）、苏珊·理查兹（Susan Richards）以及保罗·希尔德（Paul Hilder<ref name="Hayes2010">{{cite book|author=David Hayes|title=Europe: Visions, Realities, Futures|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=VR92AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA204|date=February 2010|publisher=Lulu.com|isbn=978-0-9556775-0-2|pages=204–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-08-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802073633/https://books.google.com/books?id=VR92AgAAQBAJ&pg=PA204}}</ref>）等人共同创办。该网站的口号是“自由思考、纵论世界”（free thinking for the world）<ref name="Oliver2007">{{cite book|author=Kelly Oliver|title=Women as Weapons of War: Iraq, Sex, and the Media|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=DmeTAIgce5IC&pg=PA186|date=2 November 2007|publisher=Columbia University Press|isbn=978-0-231-51245-9|pages=186–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001094116/https://books.google.com/books?id=DmeTAIgce5IC&pg=PA186}}</ref>。

开放民主网声称通过对社会和政治问题的报道和分析以寻求在全世界范围内“挑战[[权力|权力]]和鼓励[[民主|民主]][[辩论|辩论]]”（challenge power and encourage democratic debate）<ref name="Abjorensen2019">{{cite book|author=Norman Abjorensen|title=Historical Dictionary of Democracy|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cNSSDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA270|date=15 June 2019|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield|isbn=978-1-5381-2074-3|pages=270–|access-date=2020-07-04|archive-date=2021-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211102133039/https://books.google.com/books?id=cNSSDwAAQBAJ&pg=PA270}}</ref>。该网站每年吸引了约800万次点击，网站的创始人曾参与过知名媒体和政治活动。该网站得到了[[查尔斯·斯图尔特·莫特基金会|查尔斯·斯图尔特·莫特基金会]]（Charles Stewart Mott Foundation）和[[开放社会基金会|开放社会基金会]]、[[美国国家民主基金会|美国国家民主基金会]]、[[福特基金会|福特基金会]]和[[约瑟夫·罗恩特里慈善信托基金会|约瑟夫·罗恩特里慈善信托基金会]]（Joseph Rowntree Charitable Trust）等其他组织的[[资助|资助]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://opendemocracy.net/about/supporters|title=openDemocracy's Supporters|date=2014-10-01|website=[[openDemocracy|openDemocracy]]|language=|access-date=|archive-date=2019-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190226222003/https://www.opendemocracy.net/about/supporters}}</ref>。

